WEBVTT

01:56.400 --> 01:59.600
When you see these flowers
after you go back,

01:59.680 --> 02:02.760
maybe you'll think of me.

02:42.240 --> 02:43.800
Give Ji Ling back to me.

02:44.400 --> 02:45.680
Give him back!

03:36.360 --> 03:37.320
Submit.

04:02.400 --> 04:03.640
I won't kill you.

04:05.080 --> 04:06.640
But I want to kill you.

04:16.480 --> 04:18.120
You killed Ji Ling.

04:23.560 --> 04:25.040
I'm going to avenge him.

04:26.120 --> 04:27.600
You used the wrong word.

04:28.200 --> 04:30.480
To kill is to take the life
of a living being.

04:31.160 --> 04:32.840
Ji Ling was only ever a puppet.

04:33.720 --> 04:34.920
I was the one

04:36.080 --> 04:38.000
who gave him life.

04:38.680 --> 04:41.080
I merely took back what was mine.

04:42.800 --> 04:43.680
Just as I thought.

04:44.960 --> 04:47.440
You've already been corrupted by evil

04:47.520 --> 04:48.600
and strayed from the divine path.

04:50.160 --> 04:51.960
You don't deserve
the title of Dragon Deity.

04:54.120 --> 04:55.680
You also deceived Wangyan

04:55.760 --> 04:57.400
and used her to achieve your goals.

04:58.360 --> 04:59.520
Don't try to deny it.

05:00.720 --> 05:03.120
That repulsive scent on you is something

05:04.680 --> 05:06.480
I'll never forget.

05:09.680 --> 05:15.200
Wangyan, why do you carry
a strange scent today?

05:16.080 --> 05:17.720
You met her in secret.

05:18.360 --> 05:21.680
Otherwise, how could she
have caught that scent?

05:22.360 --> 05:23.400
So,

05:24.960 --> 05:26.920
you took Wu Wangyan's token

05:28.440 --> 05:29.840
to come settle the score with me?

05:30.560 --> 05:31.840
Who's to say

05:34.080 --> 05:35.440
she didn't give it to me?

05:37.720 --> 05:39.280
She would never give it to you.

05:41.040 --> 05:42.720
What exactly do you want her to do?

05:48.760 --> 05:50.400
You two are close.

05:51.680 --> 05:53.320
Why don't you ask her yourself?

05:59.720 --> 06:00.800
You don't dare.

06:02.040 --> 06:03.520
Because you're afraid.

06:04.120 --> 06:06.720
Afraid you'll hear
an answer you don't want.

06:07.360 --> 06:09.600
Afraid she's already betrayed
the Formless Moon Sect.

06:10.200 --> 06:12.160
And afraid the sisterly bond
between you two will be severed forever.

06:12.240 --> 06:13.680
Shut up.

06:15.760 --> 06:18.920
No one has ever dared
to be so insolent before me.

06:23.400 --> 06:25.160
Aren't you afraid I'll kill you?

06:26.800 --> 06:27.800
Do you think

06:29.040 --> 06:30.560
you're the only immortal one?

06:31.880 --> 06:35.120
As a Formless Moon member, even if I die,

06:35.200 --> 06:37.680
once my skin, hair, blood, and bones

06:38.560 --> 06:41.000
are dissolved
in the Primordial Sacred Spring,

06:42.920 --> 06:44.280
I can be reborn.

06:45.960 --> 06:50.480
Then what if your skin, hair,
blood, and bones

06:51.080 --> 06:52.960
are imprisoned here forever?

07:16.320 --> 07:17.360
Leave.

07:25.640 --> 07:27.280
Tell me your scheme.

08:01.760 --> 08:03.760
Stay by my side and obey me.

08:07.000 --> 08:08.600
Look how weak you are.

08:09.560 --> 08:10.800
Stop fighting.

08:12.280 --> 08:13.960
Stay in the Shilin Sect.

08:14.920 --> 08:16.400
Don't go back and report this.

08:17.880 --> 08:19.960
Don't let my plan fail.

09:27.680 --> 09:29.360
Didn't your sister go look for food?

09:30.200 --> 09:31.360
Why isn't she back yet?

09:42.160 --> 09:44.080
Weren't you supposed to go with me
to find the Dragon Deity's Power?

09:45.800 --> 09:47.240
What act are you putting on now?

09:50.280 --> 09:51.320
Relax.

09:52.760 --> 09:56.120
Once I find Wuyi, I'll come right back

09:56.200 --> 09:59.840
and tell you where the next strand
of the Dragon Deity's Power is.

10:00.440 --> 10:02.120
What if you don't come back?

10:07.720 --> 10:09.400
This is a Moon Summoning Pearl.

10:10.640 --> 10:12.960
Hold it and channel
your sacred power into it,

10:15.280 --> 10:16.760
and no matter how far away I am,

10:17.880 --> 10:20.440
you'll summon me
straight back to your side.

10:31.440 --> 10:32.280
I'll believe you one more time.

10:43.040 --> 10:44.800
Could you go wash up?

10:45.480 --> 10:46.840
You stink.

10:48.800 --> 10:50.000
Didn't I just bathe?

11:03.080 --> 11:04.960
I really can't keep
carrying you around anymore.

11:06.720 --> 11:08.320
Your stink is driving all the women away.

11:13.400 --> 11:14.440
Wu Shiguang,

11:15.640 --> 11:16.560
you're done for.

11:17.160 --> 11:18.320
You're in for some real suffering.

11:20.040 --> 11:23.080
The sourness of love
and the bitterness of longing…

11:24.560 --> 11:26.520
Do you know how people are named?

11:27.560 --> 11:30.240
They're usually named to make up
for what they lack.

11:32.920 --> 11:34.080
What do you mean?

11:35.320 --> 11:36.240
Your name "Chi", meaning "shame".

11:37.120 --> 11:38.160
Because you are shameless.

12:18.400 --> 12:19.680
Show yourself.

12:22.320 --> 12:26.000
SI FENG, GREEDY WOLF DEMON
HUNTER OF THE NORTHERN DIPPER

12:30.280 --> 12:31.520
It's been over a century,

12:31.600 --> 12:35.560
and you old demon
still love playing these spooky tricks.

12:36.600 --> 12:39.240
I'm a double-flower hunter
of the Shilin Sect.

12:39.320 --> 12:40.440
I'm a human.

12:40.520 --> 12:42.320
You are the demon.

12:43.920 --> 12:45.160
I've never seen a human

12:45.240 --> 12:48.840
turn half their body into a puppet.

12:49.600 --> 12:51.760
And at your age,

12:51.840 --> 12:53.360
you still look this young.

12:53.440 --> 12:54.680
Your beauty-preserving arts

12:54.760 --> 12:56.280
are even better than
a demon's skin-changing tricks.

12:58.040 --> 12:59.720
Just what you'd expect from a fox demon.

13:00.400 --> 13:03.040
Even your insults sound flattering.

13:03.120 --> 13:04.040
Tell me.

13:04.120 --> 13:06.600
Why did you burn
a summoning talisman to call me out here

13:06.680 --> 13:07.560
in the middle of the night?

13:08.240 --> 13:09.280
To catch up?

13:10.520 --> 13:13.120
My sister took my Shilin Sect token.

13:13.200 --> 13:14.880
She must've been growing suspicious.

13:16.240 --> 13:17.640
I'm afraid she'll find out

13:18.520 --> 13:20.600
I've been working
with the Dragon Deity all along.

13:22.720 --> 13:26.280
Master Chi Wen is stern
and ruthless in all he does.

13:27.360 --> 13:28.520
Your sister is in serious trouble.

13:45.600 --> 13:47.320
Word Magic

13:47.400 --> 13:50.200
only works on those
whose power is weaker than yours.

13:51.200 --> 13:53.320
Otherwise, the blowback
can leave you gravely injured.

13:54.760 --> 13:57.960
And once the target is on guard,

13:58.800 --> 14:00.640
Word Magic hardly works.

14:01.640 --> 14:04.240
Xiaowei's Word Magic was unrivaled.

14:04.320 --> 14:05.680
I carry Xiaowei's power.

14:07.640 --> 14:09.240
How dare you try

14:10.600 --> 14:11.640
to control me?

14:17.480 --> 14:18.680
Ji Ling…

14:30.080 --> 14:31.240
There are many restrictions
within the Shilin Sect.

14:32.160 --> 14:33.440
If you don't want your soul annihilated,

14:34.600 --> 14:35.640
stay here.

14:44.680 --> 14:47.320
TOKEN OF SCALES

15:16.440 --> 15:17.560
Here.

15:24.480 --> 15:26.880
<i>These flowers only bloom</i>
<i>in the Shilin Sect.</i>

15:27.560 --> 15:28.600
<i>They're special.</i>

16:51.480 --> 16:52.760
<i>Then let me take you somewhere.</i>

16:52.840 --> 16:54.000
<i>I'm sure it'll cheer you up.</i>

17:05.800 --> 17:09.040
I grew up by Yumian Lake.

17:09.640 --> 17:12.119
There are lots
of delicious raspberries here.

17:13.200 --> 17:14.520
I'll pick some for you in a bit.

17:25.920 --> 17:27.400
Are you sleepy?

17:28.440 --> 17:31.600
Or are you tired
of me talking about all this?

17:32.120 --> 17:33.280
No.

17:35.800 --> 17:36.920
It's just that I hate blood.

17:37.600 --> 17:39.560
I don't want to see blood on my hands.

17:43.720 --> 17:46.040
This world is such a mess.

17:46.120 --> 17:48.560
There are so many things
I don't want to see either.

17:48.640 --> 17:51.800
Death, separation,

17:52.480 --> 17:53.560
injured animals,

17:53.640 --> 17:55.680
forests burned down by mountain fires,

17:55.760 --> 17:57.000
and so many other things.

17:57.080 --> 17:58.600
I couldn't bear to look at them.

18:01.480 --> 18:02.720
But then,

18:02.800 --> 18:04.920
I learned a very useful spell.

18:06.240 --> 18:07.280
What spell?

18:08.240 --> 18:09.800
Make a circle with your hand

18:10.720 --> 18:12.600
and only look at what you like.

19:27.240 --> 19:29.720
I picked these out for you. They're sweet.

19:37.840 --> 19:38.800
Here.

19:40.640 --> 19:42.840
A bouquet of fresh wildflowers

19:42.920 --> 19:44.840
fully in bloom.

19:45.480 --> 19:46.600
Cheer up.

20:00.560 --> 20:01.520
Forget me.

20:38.600 --> 20:39.800
Why are you crying?

20:49.400 --> 20:50.680
I'm not.

20:52.520 --> 20:54.520
Then why are your eyes red?

20:57.240 --> 21:00.280
A pungent smell irritated them.

21:01.880 --> 21:03.960
You've been making things up.

21:04.040 --> 21:06.240
Why do you keep saying I carry

21:06.760 --> 21:08.360
a strange scent?

21:09.760 --> 21:10.800
Making things up?

21:13.120 --> 21:14.560
Can't you smell it yourself?

21:16.040 --> 21:17.920
I follow a vegetarian diet,

21:18.000 --> 21:19.880
and I bathe and change clothes every day.

21:19.960 --> 21:21.120
Other than you,

21:21.200 --> 21:24.640
no one has ever said
there's anything strange about my scent.

21:25.960 --> 21:28.320
Maybe they've been around you so long

21:28.400 --> 21:29.600
their sense of smell has gone wrong.

21:30.280 --> 21:33.680
Don't be insolent before me.

21:34.960 --> 21:36.600
How long are you going to keep me here?

21:46.440 --> 21:47.600
This won't work.

21:48.320 --> 21:49.920
On the next night of the full moon,

21:50.000 --> 21:52.960
the Oracle Stone's power
will summon me back to the Formless Moon.

21:53.720 --> 21:55.760
Do you really think you can trap me

21:56.960 --> 21:58.000
in this pathetic sect?

22:02.000 --> 22:03.480
You can try.

22:08.120 --> 22:09.040
Ji Ling.

22:12.440 --> 22:14.080
Will I ever see him again?

22:17.280 --> 22:18.480
Didn't you say

22:22.920 --> 22:24.240
I was him?

22:27.960 --> 22:30.600
I want to see the Ji Ling
who always had a smile on his face,

22:32.480 --> 22:34.360
who was warm and kind.

22:36.480 --> 22:37.800
Am I never

22:41.040 --> 22:42.600
going to see him again?

23:23.640 --> 23:26.840
People worship you
and place their faith in you,

23:27.760 --> 23:31.200
never knowing you've long lost
your mercy and divinity.

23:32.000 --> 23:34.360
And you still had the nerve
to put up your own statue here

23:34.880 --> 23:38.480
to receive offerings, bows,
and worship from the hunters?

23:41.360 --> 23:43.120
Shameless.

24:41.400 --> 24:43.480
Lu Wuyi really is fearless.

24:44.440 --> 24:47.040
A demon barging into the Shilin Sect?

24:47.120 --> 24:48.640
How's that different from a chicken

24:48.720 --> 24:51.080
charging into a weasel's den
and crowing at the top of its lungs?

24:51.160 --> 24:53.960
Still, someone as mighty
as the Dragon Deity

24:54.040 --> 24:56.560
wouldn't lock up a young girl
and torture her,

24:57.360 --> 24:58.440
would he?

25:00.400 --> 25:03.120
Hasn't he done plenty of evil already?

25:03.200 --> 25:07.000
But surely he'd at least feed her, right?

25:09.520 --> 25:10.680
The food at the Shilin Sect

25:11.960 --> 25:13.120
doesn't even have a drop of oil in it.

25:14.640 --> 25:15.760
Even dogs wouldn't eat it.

25:57.920 --> 26:00.080
I fell asleep
in the Dragon Deity Palace last night.

26:00.160 --> 26:01.480
Which one of you brought me back?

26:02.360 --> 26:04.320
The Dragon Deity Palace
is a solemn, sacred place.

26:04.400 --> 26:05.840
You're not allowed to sleep there.

26:07.880 --> 26:09.680
I… I brought you back.

26:10.280 --> 26:13.040
I used magic to bring you back.

26:14.760 --> 26:15.600
You?

26:20.440 --> 26:21.480
Me.

26:23.480 --> 26:24.680
What's your name?

26:26.320 --> 26:27.280
My name is Ye Changsheng.

26:27.360 --> 26:29.640
I'm Master Chi Wen's attendant.

26:29.720 --> 26:30.920
My grandfather was an attendant too.

26:31.000 --> 26:33.960
My family has served
Master Chi Wen for three generations.

26:36.320 --> 26:37.480
Ye Changsheng?

26:39.000 --> 26:40.880
I'm a fox demon that eats people.

26:43.280 --> 26:44.920
If you stick around,
you can kiss longevity goodbye.

26:45.000 --> 26:46.200
I…

26:47.040 --> 26:48.640
Breakfast is ready, Miss Lu.

26:49.400 --> 26:51.320
I bought all this
from a restaurant outside,

26:51.400 --> 26:53.360
since our food may be
too light for your liking.

26:53.440 --> 26:54.520
Take a look.

26:56.000 --> 26:57.320
Did Chi Wen tell you to buy this?

27:01.080 --> 27:02.560
I… I bought it myself.

27:02.640 --> 27:04.040
You?

27:05.000 --> 27:06.720
What, do you like me?

27:06.800 --> 27:07.680
No…

27:07.760 --> 27:09.800
Miss, please don't say
things like that. I…

27:10.880 --> 27:12.600
Does it suit your taste?
If there's nothing else,

27:12.680 --> 27:13.800
I'll be going now.

27:23.920 --> 27:25.720
Why aren't you eating?

27:27.080 --> 27:28.160
I'm worried you poisoned it.

27:40.520 --> 27:42.280
Then I really don't get it.

27:42.840 --> 27:45.320
You lock me up here as a prisoner.

27:46.240 --> 27:48.800
Why did you prepare such a feast for me?

27:49.480 --> 27:51.280
Master Chi Wen only said

27:51.360 --> 27:53.560
you'd be staying at the Shilin Sect
for a while.

27:53.640 --> 27:55.120
He never said you were a prisoner.

27:56.280 --> 27:58.000
I can't even move around at will.

27:58.080 --> 27:59.240
If I'm not a prisoner, what am I?

27:59.880 --> 28:01.320
The only thing missing
is a pair of shackles.

28:02.320 --> 28:03.920
Where is Chi Wen?

28:05.240 --> 28:08.040
I can't finish
all this good food by myself.

28:08.640 --> 28:09.520
Tell him to come eat with me.

28:10.200 --> 28:12.800
Master Chi Wen never dines with others.

28:12.880 --> 28:15.680
Normally, Commander Li attends
to Master Chi Wen during meals,

28:15.760 --> 28:18.680
because there are simply
too many demons who want to harm him.

28:18.760 --> 28:21.400
To be safe, he only eats food
delivered by Commander Li.

28:21.480 --> 28:22.600
No exceptions.

28:22.680 --> 28:23.960
But

28:25.120 --> 28:27.400
only a dragon can kill a dragon.

28:28.040 --> 28:30.240
Why would he worry
about others poisoning him?

28:30.320 --> 28:34.040
Even if the poison wouldn't kill him,
it would still feel awful.

28:55.600 --> 28:56.960
Is it that bad?

28:59.960 --> 29:01.000
It's so good.

29:01.600 --> 29:04.640
Back at the Formless Moon,
we could only eat fruits and vegetables.

29:04.720 --> 29:06.480
But here, you're feeding me so well.

29:06.560 --> 29:07.880
Now that I've tasted luxury,

29:08.480 --> 29:11.760
how am I supposed
to go back to eating simple meals?

29:11.840 --> 29:12.840
I… I'll take my leave now.

29:20.280 --> 29:21.400
It's already morning.

29:22.240 --> 29:23.520
I've been trying
to reassure you all night.

29:23.600 --> 29:25.200
Why are you still so worried?

29:26.200 --> 29:29.240
Wuyi has never suffered or been wronged
a day in her life.

29:30.120 --> 29:33.120
She's probably being tortured
at the Shilin Sect right now.

29:39.160 --> 29:42.880
Yunjin brocade quilts
and a soft pillow made of golden silk.

29:42.960 --> 29:45.080
Are these to your liking, Miss Lu?

29:46.280 --> 29:48.040
This is nowhere near
as nice as what we have

29:48.120 --> 29:49.880
at the Formless Moon.

29:49.960 --> 29:53.680
This is already the best
the Shilin Sect can offer.

29:55.600 --> 29:56.680
The best?

29:58.400 --> 30:00.200
What good are pillows and quilts alone?

30:00.800 --> 30:02.400
I don't even have a change of clothes.

30:03.080 --> 30:05.120
All I have is this shabby robe.

30:05.960 --> 30:06.880
It's hideous.

30:06.960 --> 30:09.680
This isn't some shabby robe.

30:09.760 --> 30:11.760
<i>It's… It's…</i>

30:18.760 --> 30:20.760
Do you have any other requests, Miss Lu?

30:20.840 --> 30:23.080
Master Chi Wen said
we were to do whatever you ask.

30:23.160 --> 30:25.480
So what exactly is he playing at?

30:25.560 --> 30:27.360
A stick, and then a carrot?

30:28.040 --> 30:29.560
Save it.

30:29.640 --> 30:32.120
I don't accept charity.
Let me make one thing clear.

30:32.960 --> 30:35.440
Don't think you can wear down my resolve

30:36.440 --> 30:38.760
with fine clothes and good food.

30:38.840 --> 30:40.160
<i>Even if the Dragon Deity</i>
<i>doesn't mistreat her,</i>

30:40.240 --> 30:42.040
there are so many hunters
in the Shilin Sect

30:42.120 --> 30:43.360
who hate demons to the bone.

30:43.440 --> 30:46.720
<i>They'll definitely bully Wuyi in secret.</i>

30:47.720 --> 30:51.160
Miss Lu, are you pleased
with this incense?

30:56.160 --> 30:57.560
It smells wonderful.

30:58.440 --> 30:59.920
Life at the Shilin Sect

31:00.600 --> 31:02.000
is way too comfortable.

31:02.080 --> 31:04.560
Fine. I promise.

31:04.640 --> 31:05.880
I'll go back to the Shilin Sect
and check on her for you.

31:06.720 --> 31:09.760
But the next full moon is almost here.

31:09.840 --> 31:11.600
Your memories will be shared
at the Sacred Spring.

31:11.680 --> 31:13.400
How are you going to keep
your secrets from the other members?

31:14.920 --> 31:17.000
It doesn't matter. At worst,

31:17.680 --> 31:20.000
I'll do what Xiaowei did
and cut off a tail to survive.

31:21.000 --> 31:22.880
The Never-Ending Curse
will hunt you forever.

31:22.960 --> 31:25.520
You'll have to lose a sense,
live in anonymity,

31:25.600 --> 31:28.240
and become an ordinary woman
who doesn't dare use demon magic.

31:28.320 --> 31:29.160
Do you really want that?

31:30.320 --> 31:31.400
Living like a mortal

31:32.720 --> 31:34.240
is exactly what I've always wanted.

31:35.640 --> 31:38.360
Chi Wen thinks I'm some demoness

31:38.440 --> 31:41.080
who has done all kinds of evil
and endangered the people,

31:41.880 --> 31:43.960
so he locked me up in the Shilin Sect.

31:44.920 --> 31:46.480
But as a demon,

31:47.280 --> 31:50.080
I'm not used to sleeping
on Yunjin brocade and fine silk.

31:51.200 --> 31:55.000
Then… Then what are you
used to sleeping on, Miss Lu?

31:57.400 --> 31:58.520
As a demon,

31:59.520 --> 32:00.520
of course, I'm used to sleeping

32:00.600 --> 32:02.960
on things far bloodier
and more terrifying.

32:03.040 --> 32:04.560
It helps with cultivating demon magic.

32:05.320 --> 32:06.280
For example,

32:08.000 --> 32:08.960
human skin.

32:09.880 --> 32:10.920
What?

32:19.600 --> 32:20.920
You've got some nerve.

32:22.720 --> 32:26.560
I heard Chi Wen
was injured in a brutal battle

32:27.160 --> 32:28.520
and needed to absorb
humans' life force to recover.

32:28.600 --> 32:30.720
Miss Lu, you mustn't speak nonsense.

32:30.800 --> 32:33.040
Master Chi Wen is the Dragon Deity
who protects all living beings.

32:33.120 --> 32:34.920
He holds kindness and compassion

32:35.000 --> 32:36.640
for every creature in the world.

32:37.600 --> 32:38.560
You must not slander him.

32:39.920 --> 32:42.040
I didn't realize
you were this loyal to Chi Wen.

32:43.320 --> 32:45.200
When we of the Formless Moon
carried out missions,

32:45.880 --> 32:48.800
we disguised ourselves
as Shilin Sect members more than once.

32:48.880 --> 32:52.560
I like how smooth your skin is.

32:52.640 --> 32:54.320
When I get the chance
next time, I'll use it.

32:54.400 --> 32:56.000
Give it to me.

32:56.640 --> 32:58.520
Master Chi Wen, help!

33:05.760 --> 33:07.200
You can trap me here,

33:08.200 --> 33:10.920
but no one in the Shilin Sect
is getting any peace either.

33:13.520 --> 33:17.240
Let's torture each other
and see who lasts longer.

33:32.600 --> 33:34.320
It's just been one night,

33:35.040 --> 33:36.640
Shiguang,

33:37.760 --> 33:41.040
and you already can't resist using

33:41.880 --> 33:43.200
my Moon Summoning Pearl?

33:46.520 --> 33:48.040
Did you miss me that much?

33:51.560 --> 33:53.120
Do all you foxes from the Formless Moon

33:54.120 --> 33:58.440
talk in this halting, syrupy way?

34:04.160 --> 34:05.240
Where's Lu Wuyi?

34:07.480 --> 34:09.040
She's grown up and gotten rebellious.

34:10.199 --> 34:12.560
She has ideas of her own. Let's go.

34:14.280 --> 34:15.560
Go where?

34:16.520 --> 34:17.719
The Ruined Sand.

34:18.400 --> 34:20.280
That's where the next strand

34:21.280 --> 34:23.520
of the Dragon Deity's Power is.

34:24.400 --> 34:27.360
Help him. Earn his trust.

34:28.600 --> 34:29.639
Then

34:31.000 --> 34:32.199
take the prayer beads.

34:36.280 --> 34:37.320
What is it?

34:38.080 --> 34:39.440
You know that place?

34:56.400 --> 34:58.000
No return.

34:58.800 --> 35:00.320
No finding it again.

35:02.680 --> 35:04.600
No matter how many times
I perform the divination,

35:06.600 --> 35:07.760
the result

35:09.840 --> 35:11.200
is always the same.

35:19.280 --> 35:20.960
How much longer are you going to wait

35:21.040 --> 35:23.000
before you fulfill your promise

35:23.080 --> 35:25.040
and make the Star Stone shine again?

35:34.440 --> 35:36.160
You said that once
the Star Stone became whole,

35:36.960 --> 35:38.520
it would shine again

35:41.880 --> 35:42.800
and free my people

35:43.480 --> 35:45.880
from the Petrification Curse.

35:45.960 --> 35:48.080
That's why I broke my oath

35:48.160 --> 35:50.360
and took back the power
I lent the Dragon Deity.

35:51.720 --> 35:52.600
So why

35:58.480 --> 36:00.120
isn't it working?

36:06.800 --> 36:10.000
Because we still have to wait
for the man with the Twelve Thoughts.

36:35.520 --> 36:37.440
Don't you get bored
sitting in meditation all day?

36:38.680 --> 36:41.480
Come pick some
fresh flowers with me, will you?

36:42.560 --> 36:43.440
No.

36:45.320 --> 36:46.520
Then I'll go by myself.

36:46.600 --> 36:47.680
Stop.

36:50.160 --> 36:51.360
You're not going either.

36:52.640 --> 36:54.520
Don't force me to use
Word Magic on you again.

36:58.440 --> 37:00.520
My power may be weaker than yours,

37:01.120 --> 37:04.200
but I'm on guard
against you every second now.

37:04.280 --> 37:05.320
It won't be that easy

37:06.600 --> 37:07.600
for you to control me.

37:22.320 --> 37:24.200
That demoness defiled
the Dragon Deity's statue.

37:24.280 --> 37:26.440
I've been scrubbing it for three days,
and it still won't come clean.

37:26.520 --> 37:27.720
She's infuriating!

37:31.200 --> 37:33.040
Please, stop drawing on it!

37:43.520 --> 37:45.640
She said she wanted rootless water.

37:45.720 --> 37:48.120
I want rootless water,

37:48.960 --> 37:50.560
dustless fruit,

37:52.320 --> 37:53.520
and scentless incense.

37:53.600 --> 37:55.120
How was I supposed
to know what those were?

37:55.200 --> 37:57.160
She was obviously
making things difficult on purpose.

37:57.240 --> 37:58.840
She said I peeked while she was changing.

37:58.920 --> 38:01.120
Good grief! Who changes clothes
in the hallway?

38:04.120 --> 38:05.160
What's wrong with you,

38:05.240 --> 38:07.320
peeking at a young girl changing clothes?

38:07.400 --> 38:08.280
How shameless.

38:09.000 --> 38:10.440
I almost gouged out my own eyes!

38:13.600 --> 38:16.280
Commander Li,
please talk to the Dragon Deity

38:16.360 --> 38:17.240
so he lets her go soon.

38:17.320 --> 38:19.360
If she doesn't leave, I will.

38:19.440 --> 38:20.640
She's unbearable,

38:20.720 --> 38:23.000
evil to the core!

38:44.920 --> 38:45.840
What's with that look?

38:48.320 --> 38:49.480
Three words

38:50.040 --> 38:52.160
describe you perfectly right now.

38:57.560 --> 38:58.560
Which three?

39:00.040 --> 39:01.040
Undignified old man.

39:03.880 --> 39:05.040
I…

39:11.640 --> 39:12.480
VIRTUE COMMANDS, EVIL YIELDS

39:18.600 --> 39:21.520
This is no sparring match.
This is bullying!

39:22.320 --> 39:24.600
Chi Wen has such a good temper.

39:25.360 --> 39:27.000
I've caused this much commotion,

39:27.080 --> 39:28.560
and he still won't come out to stop me.

39:28.640 --> 39:30.320
If he won't stop you, I will!

40:09.320 --> 40:11.000
This is Shilin Sect territory.

40:11.560 --> 40:13.320
How dare a demoness
like you run wild here?

40:14.400 --> 40:17.160
If you don't want me running wild,
tell him to let me go.

40:17.240 --> 40:20.400
He doesn't dare kill me for fear
of angering the Formless Moon,

40:20.480 --> 40:22.200
but he's also afraid
I'll expose his true colors,

40:22.800 --> 40:24.440
so he traps me here.

40:25.440 --> 40:26.840
But what's the point?

40:27.600 --> 40:30.160
When the full moon comes,
I'll still be able to leave.

40:30.240 --> 40:31.120
Shut up.

40:59.080 --> 41:00.640
Greetings, Master Chi Wen.

41:03.400 --> 41:04.640
Come with me.

41:06.320 --> 41:07.160
Get moving already.

41:14.160 --> 41:17.320
I was talking to you. Come with me.

41:19.840 --> 41:21.360
And if I don't want to?

41:21.960 --> 41:24.800
Are you going to tie me up,
Master Chi Wen?
